AI-RMS: Project Briefing Document
Date: April 24, 2026 | Status: Phase 1 Complete, Phase 2 Planned | Repo: github.com/RRM00/ai-rms

1. What Is AI-RMS?
AI-RMS (AI-Enhanced Restaurant Management System) is a cloud-native, Generative AI-powered Point of Sale (POS) system. It is designed as an "Agentic Web App" where LLMs actively assist in upselling, operational forecasting, and business intelligence.

Architecture: 4-Tier Decoupled System
Presentation Layer(React + Tailwind)
Logic Layer(FastAPI)
Intelligence Layer(LangChain + LLM)
Data Layer(SQLAlchemy + SQLite)
Layer	Tech	Purpose
Presentation	React, Tailwind CSS v3, Vite	POS UI, Admin Dashboard, Kitchen Display
Logic	Python, FastAPI (async)	REST API, JWT Auth, business rules
Intelligence	LangChain, OpenAI (Phase 2)	Upsell, Analytics, Sentiment, Wait-Time
Data	SQLAlchemy, SQLite (swappable to PostgreSQL)	Persistent storage, async I/O
