2.2 Backend API — 16 Endpoints
The backend runs on FastAPI with full async support, JWT authentication, and role-based access control.

Method	Endpoint	Auth	Description
POST	/api/auth/login	Public	Staff login → returns JWT token
POST	/api/auth/register	Admin	Create new staff accounts
GET	/api/auth/me	Bearer	Get current user profile
GET	/api/menu	Public	List all menu items (filterable by category)
POST	/api/menu	Admin	Create a new menu item
PATCH	/api/menu/{id}	Admin	Update item (price, availability, etc.)
DELETE	/api/menu/{id}	Admin	Remove a menu item
GET	/api/orders	Bearer	Order history with date/limit filtering
POST	/api/orders	Bearer	Create order from cart payload
GET	/api/orders/{id}	Bearer	Get a single order by ID
PATCH	/api/orders/{id}/status	Bearer	Update order status (kitchen workflow)
GET	/api/kitchen/active	Bearer	All active (non-delivered) orders
POST	/api/reviews	Public	Submit a customer review
GET	/api/reviews	Bearer	List all reviews (paginated)
GET	/	Public	Health check
