4. How to Run It
bash
# Backend (terminal 1)
cd backend
pip install -r requirements.txt
python seed.py          # Create tables + seed menu data
python -m uvicorn app.main:app --reload --port 8000
# Frontend (terminal 2)
cd frontend
npm install
npm run dev             # → http://localhost:5173
Default credentials: 
admin
 / admin123 or staff / staff123

